			<outline text="November 11" created="Tue, 11 Nov 1997 05:00:01 GMT">
				<outline text="Finally! There &lt;b&gt;is&lt;/b&gt; a way to close all the browser windows in Windows with one operation. From Faisal Jawdat  ">
